		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>Anyway, I think this deserves a thread of it's own. At any rate, especially at the high end with 9k+ pools the&nbsp; downtime is rediculous. So here are my thoughts:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>1. An aa that allows for sitting mana regeneration while sitting, or sharply increases the percentage per tick. Like increase mana regeneration 5%/10%/15% ect.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>2. Raise med skill post 65.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>3. Raise mana preservation from 20% to 25% and 30%.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>4. Increase current FT cap post 65 to 20 innately, while allowing the AA to take it to 25. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>5. Reconfigure Meditation skill instead of a specific amount of mana regeneration per tick, it goes to&nbsp; a percentile of mana per tick based on skill. This way the ability scales with mana pool.</DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							Vjik ~~wielding a giant shotgun, partnered with Pikachu, the Hamster Slayer~~<br><br>"Always late, so much hate for slow food..."
							</div>
								
		</td></tr>
