		" 
			>
			<DIV>It completely depends on the situation.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>In Hurk's situation, he tends to solo, its often better to get to FM before continuing to solo, because you never know what can happen and if you only get to 50% you could easily run oom in the wrong situation.&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>However in a group situation, Rexl and I agree.&nbsp; I typically med to 30% (of 10k mana) when I am rezzed and am able to continue without difficulty, slowly regening more than I use.&nbsp; Even when my mana pool was only 6k I would instruct my group that when I hit 50% I could continue, I simply would not do the "extra" stuff I normally do (RDS, pet, occasional nuke), and for the most part the group never notices my "extra" stuff being missing anyway.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
